2052.subject: HPWE
2052.descrlong: A daily combination of step aerobic exercise and practical information regarding health issues including fitness, nutrition and weight management, and stress reduction techniques. The course will empower students to design their own health program and monitor their progress throughout the semester. Credit/no credit option. (Offered as interest warrants.)
